1. **Studio subtype comparison table with decision framing.** Wikipedia and ILS competitors mention alcove studios in passing but do not give renters a structured comparison of all five subtypes with square footage ranges and use cases. Claude's response did this well, which means AI engines are already primed to cite a source that provides it clearly. This article should own that citation position.

